# Installation

This project is managed by uv. Hence these are some steps to follow for setup.

```bash
# Create a virtual env
python3 -m venv .venv

# Activate the virtual environment
source .venv/bin/activate

# UV install
uv sync

# CLI installation (check pyproject.toml)
uv pip install -e . Or task install
```

```bash
# To run service cli
uv task service
  
```


## Docker Stack

```bash
# Start services
docker-compose up -d

# View logs
docker-compose logs -f

# Stop services
docker-compose down

# Stop and remove volume (ideal for removing cache)
docker-compose down -v
```
